Package com.gmail.woodyc40.commons.collect Description

Collections and custom implementation frameworks using the JCF

These are mainly just for play, usually being slower than the collections tuned by Sun engineers.

There are a few helper classes that may come in handy however, and a few classes with a better hash distribution implementing the Murmur3 32bit used in Google Guava, or switchable.

No class in this package are thread safe.
